  "body": "***Type***: Bug\r\n\r\n*Summary*: Users connected to any of `Status Mailservers A`, `Status Mailservers B` or `Status Mailservers C` with the **Ropsten** network keep getting 'Failed to connect to mailserver. Tap to reconnect'. Offline inbox for this settings doesn't work.\r\n\r\nNote: it's all **fine on Mainnet** for any mailserver (including A B and C), but fails for Ropsten. Node version for app build is a339d7e\r\n\r\nNote2: recently we fixed the issue with Mailservers A B and C with the https://github.com/status-im/status-react/commit/96628caa9ede2f9eca8405b84c792f3134245833 update. \r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\nOffline inbox works for Mailservers A, B and C when a user connected via Ropsten network\r\n\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\nOffline inboxing doesn't work under Mailservers A, B and C with the Ropsten\r\n\r\n### Reproduction\r\n\r\n- Open Status and create new account\r\n- Navigate to Profile -> Mailserver -> set any of mailservers A / B / C\r\n- Navigate to Profile -> Network -> connect to 'Ropsten with upstream RPC' network\r\n- Log in to the same account and join '#status' public channel\r\n- Check that chat history got fetched and appears for public chat you joined \r\n- Wait +1.5 minute staying on chat screen/Home screen\r\n- Check there is no `Could not connect to mailserver. Tap to reconnect` label appears at the top of the screen\r\n- _(Optional)_ Now switch account to `Mainnet with upstream RPC` network and re-login to the same account. Stay +1.5 minute to check whether there is no `Could not connect to mailserver. Tap to reconnect` notification.\r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n* Status version: Develop 0.9.21 (6181) node a339d7e (jenkins nightly 486th build from 9th of July)\r\n* Operating System: Android and iOS\r\n\r\n#### Logs\r\n\r\nSee TF logs and geth.log for above scenario on Android session: https://app.testfairy.com/projects/4803622-status/builds/8518521/sessions/4395882172/?accessToken=T1nd47FPhE6sJdGWq65nmSAbWu4\r\n\r\nGeth.log above TF session:\r\n[gethlog.log](https://github.com/status-im/status-react/files/2176061/gethlog.log)\r\n\n\n<blockquote><div><strong><a href=\"https://app.testfairy.com/projects/4803622-status/builds/8518521/sessions/4395882172/?accessToken=T1nd47FPhE6sJdGWq65nmSAbWu4\">TestFairy: Status 0.9.21 (6181) @2018</a></strong></div></blockquote>",
